## To setup your own Ethereum Node

 - Install `geth` by following the official <a href="https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Building-Ethereum" target="_blank">instructions</a>
 - Start Ethereum node with RPC by running the command
 
 
```
geth --rpcapi="db,eth,net,web3,personal,web3" --rpc
```

 
## RPC will be exposed on
 - 127.0.0.1 port 8545
 
 - If you want to change host and port, use 


```
 geth --rpcapi="db,eth,net,web3,personal,web3" --rpc --rpcaddr <ip> --rpcport <portnumber>` 
```

